name: made sangketan room
address: H3FW+QH3, Sangketan, Penebel, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82152, Indonesia
review 1: really bad, the roofs have many leaks, the kitchen is totally rotten, the water supply is instable, the electricity is low, no wifi, the next supermarket is 40 minutes away in Tabanan, the next (small) local market (Penatahan) 20 minutes away (open at 6 in the morning and 6 in the evening), the road up here is very bad, more holes then anything else, a lot of chainsaw noise.. they want you to live like the locals, but pay like a boule.. cannot recommend this place..
